{"tid":488772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【千億鐵路】田北辰稱可接受沙中綫超支150億 料港鐵不願為造價封頂","createTime":"2017-12-04T04:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T01:20:30.000Z","uid":138214,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1d346f38dc26a4ef4138a3c3bdc02a8744305a7b","tid":488772,"uid":138214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171204/large/1512358443_f27b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171204%2Flarge%2F1512358443_f27b.jpg&h=2e04a798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中綫工程超支，金額將於月內公佈，立法會鐵路事宜小組主席田北辰在電台節目上指，沙中綫涉及多個車站，工程被廣深港高鐵複雜，故最終若超支額為150億左右，亦勉強可接受。但他亦指港鐵工程需要2021年才完成，期間難掌控所有情況，故估計港鐵未必願意為造價封頂。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰在節目中指，該項目以「先撥款，後招標」形式推行，同時本港又正進行多個基建工程，故因此推高招標價格，而由於沙中綫項目為期７年，屬長期工程，故政府只能以當時市價估算，故容易造成超支。他建議日後短期基工程應採用「先招標，後撥款」方式進行，以免日後估價與實際工程金額相差太遠。<br />\n田又指，沙中綫工程有多個外在因素影響進度，故要證明港鐵在有關項目上有失誤的難度很高，但不排除政府與港鐵日後會就沙中綫項目有仲裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171204/57538574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57538574&d=jmZZ4DKXYc0ad%2BXFGFcfwE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a47a1c00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57538574&h=b880fe8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171204/57538574</a><br />\n<br />\n痴撚左線？ 用成千億整條沙中線 咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b4725b986cc1e393109eb0d7ff2bbc95d19f85","tid":488772,"uid":46049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"過千億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk