ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2805ab0089da4248fa8ece886c2fbbdce8bb6dc5","tid":488772,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地鐵起碼香港人常用，方便到大家生活都值嘅，用三十年都回本，港豬澳 高鐵真係一世無機會用</blockquote><br />\n千億三十年真係可以回本？</blockquote><br />\n&quot;Based on the direct economic benefits generated from the SCL alone, we estimate that the economic internal rate of return (EIRR) of the SCL project will be 6%. For other railway projects that have been recently implemented, namely the KTE, SIL(E), Hong Kong section of the Guangzhou=Shenzhen-Hong Kong Express Rail Link (XRL) and West Island Line, their EIRRs are 7%, 6%, 6% and 5% respectively.&quot; <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr11-12/english/fc/pwsc/papers/p12-01e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr11-12%2Fenglish%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fpapers%2Fp12-01e.pdf&d=jmZZ4DKXYc0ad%2BXFGFcfwE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=52e07a72\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr11-12/english/fc/pwsc/papers/p12-01e.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"5fd64c808ebb1a2cfaa2c800611161dcc26ea9a9","tid":488772,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地鐵起碼香港人常用，方便到大家生活都值嘅，用三十年都回本，港豬澳 高鐵真係一世無機會用</blockquote><br />\n千億三十年真係可以回本？</blockquote><br />\n&quot;Based on the direct economic benefits generated from the SCL alone, we estimate that the economic internal rate of return (EIRR) of the SCL project will be 6%. For other railway projects that have been recently implemented, namely the KTE, SIL(E), Hong Kong section of the Guangzhou=Shenzhen-Hong Kong Express Rail Link (XRL) and West Island Line, their EIRRs are 7%, 6%, 6% and 5% respectively.&quot; <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr11-12/english/fc/pwsc/papers/p12-01e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr11-12%2Fenglish%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fpapers%2Fp12-01e.pdf&d=jmZZ4DKXYc0ad%2BXFGFcfwE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=52e07a72\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr11-12/english/fc/pwsc/papers/p12-01e.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f04f1d9abe894380377451b68d501ea01ddb61","tid":488772,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:25:06.000Z","msg":"食屎大"},{"pid":"fe33267d0783335bb967c5ff06261ca8d1289f6f","tid":488772,"uid":39700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵起碼香港人常用，方便到大家生活都值嘅，用三十年都回本，港豬澳 高鐵真係一世無機會用</blockquote><br />\n痴撚左線<br />\n你而家個情況就好似<br />\n以前人地比開屎你食<br />\n今日比舊好撚難食既豬扒比你<br />\n之後同佢講 我接受到 好撚好味呀<br />\n起碼食得落口<br />\n<br />\nLittle evil ?"},{"pid":"e40f1bdb6eb2ae4ed9376020b2116f5ef7e02201","tid":488772,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地鐵起碼香港人常用，方便到大家生活都值嘅，用三十年都回本，港豬澳 高鐵真係一世無機會用</blockquote><br />\n千億三十年真係可以回本？</blockquote><br />\n以前地鐵規劃果時都係大白象工程，新機場都係。<br />\n有時有d 野唔係咁樣計。<br />\n<br />\n利申 超支好離譜"},{"pid":"320125e95a1fdc0e4664981cdcd89f42f70d4ce6","tid":488772,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:09:57.000Z","msg":"香港點解起咩都會超支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac244017c2e09de8890a05f5a989eb22fa5b6781","tid":488772,"uid":15548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"唔怪得近兩三個星期係咁賣廣告講起條沙中線有幾高難度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}